  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_153",
    "english": "A member of the half-human, half-bird \"harpy\" that dwells in the Demon Realm. They have the power to control the mind, making their prey go to sleep with their cries, or break their minds. They always have a blank face, making it hard to figure out what they're thinking of.",
    "japanese": "A member of the half-human, half-bird \"harpy\" that dwells in the Demon Realm. They have the power to control the mind, making their prey go to sleep with their cries, or break their minds. They always have a blank face, making it hard to figure out what they're thinking of.",
    "korean": "A member of the half-human, half-bird \"harpy\" that dwells in the Demon Realm. They have the power to control the mind, making their prey go to sleep with their cries, or break their minds. They always have a blank face, making it hard to figure out what they're thinking of.",
    "chinese_simplified": "A member of the half-human, half-bird \"harpy\" that dwells in the Demon Realm. They have the power to control the mind, making their prey go to sleep with their cries, or break their minds. They always have a blank face, making it hard to figure out what they're thinking of.",
    "chinese_traditional": "A member of the half-human, half-bird \"harpy\" that dwells in the Demon Realm. They have the power to control the mind, making their prey go to sleep with their cries, or break their minds. They always have a blank face, making it hard to figure out what they're thinking of.",
    "spanish": "A member of the half-human, half-bird \"harpy\" that dwells in the Demon Realm. They have the power to control the mind, making their prey go to sleep with their cries, or break their minds. They always have a blank face, making it hard to figure out what they're thinking of."
